title: War of the Roses: Something Was Stuck to Her Butt
description: Brad is doing War of the Roses on his girlfriend Katie because after a "day at the pool" with her girlfriends she came home with something stuck on her that shouldn't have been if she was simply hanging at the pool.  Brad pretty much knows she's cheating, and just wants to catch her now.
